title: Lil Devil Teemo icon
body:
I beat the two doom bot modes and have yet to receive my Teemo icon? I did it when it first came out. When am I suppose to receive it?
{{champion:17}}

replies.body:
You should receive it no later than November 17th, which is the final cut off day for these. If you don't have it *after* the 17th rolls by, reach out in a [support ticket.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)

Let me know if you have any questions.
